<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الْأَنْعَام<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَفْسِيرُ السُّورَةِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{الْحَمْدُ للهِ الَّذِي خَلَقَ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضَ وَجَعَلَ الظُّلُمَاتِ وَالنُّورَ ثُمَّ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا بِرَبِّهِمْ يَعْدِلُونَ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٣ص١١:</span> <span class="c3">{يَعْدِلُونَ}</span>: يَجْعَلُونَ عَدْلًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">يُقَالُ:</span> عَدْلُ ذَلِكَ: مِثْلُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَإِذَا كُسِرَتْ <span class="c2">(عِدْلٌ)</span> فَهُوَ: زِنَةُ ذَلِكَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الأنعام: ١]</p> </div>